description: Welcome to this sun-splashed penthouse condo in the heart of South Boston offering unbeatable value, lifestyle, and investment upside. This TRUE 2-bedroom, 1-bath home features all-new stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, in-unit laundry, central AC, and a spacious open layout with a cozy gas fireplace. Step outside to enjoy two incredible private outdoor spaces, including a rear deck and an expansive roof deck with sweeping city views—perfect for entertaining or unwinding above it all. Additional perks include private basement storage and a well-maintained, three-unit building. Located just steps from the transformative 21-acre On the Dot development, this home sits in one of Southie’s most exciting growth corridors, promising strong appreciation for years to come. Walkable to Andrew Square, the Red Line, South Bay, the beach, and everything this vibrant neighborhood has to offer. This condo is the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and long-term potential.
